This is a problem in the Fitbit Android app, which is responsible for all the communication between watch and phone.

content: I tried to develop this photo gallery app for the ionic. I know fitbit smart watches are in its infancy and it's difficult to create apps for the ionic. content: Great once I got it working... Run down for how it worked straight away for me after a playing around... Set up photos on app, then sync Ionic and make sure it connects, then click to download whilst synced up, then a warning will appear on the watch about opening app, then open the app and instantly click on retry and then download... Voila, worked in 5 seconds... Hope this helps!
